mulan.evaluation.measure

Class AverageRelativeMAE

  • java.lang.Object
    • mulan.evaluation.measure.RegressionMeasureBase
      • mulan.evaluation.measure.AverageMAE
        • mulan.evaluation.measure.AverageRelativeMAE
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, MacroAverageMeasure, Measure

    public class AverageRelativeMAE
extends AverageMAE
implements MacroAverageMeasure
    Implementation of the average Relative Mean Absolute Error (RMAE) measure. RMAE for each target is equal to the MAE of the prediction divided by the MAE of predicting the mean. Two versions of this measure are implemented, one computes target means on the training set and the other on the union of the training set and the test set. The first version is the default one.
    Version:
    2013.11.08
    Author:
    Eleftherios Spyromitros-Xioufis
